data.description: Welcome home to this beautiful starter home! Perfect for any first time homebuyer! Walking in to be greeted by an open concept with the living and kitchen areas. Conveniently located in a quiet neighborhood close to schools, freeway access, and shopping. With brand new garbage disposal, brand new farm house sink, brand new dishwasher, and more. Reach out for more details!
